{"tid":1183360,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"懷疑有甲亢","createTime":"2019-06-03T00:30:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T01:44:04.000Z","uid":256872,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"eaf67c13e62a0bce62d8602299c454bd00e8756a","tid":1183360,"uid":256872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T00:30:36.000Z","msg":"我呀媽同呀婆都有甲亢，唔知自己有冇遺傳<br />\n呢兩三個月開始勁甩頭髮，尤其係洗頭吹頭果陣，一地都係頭髮，依家可能三分一頭髮冇咗<br />\n呢兩個星期又食得多野，但我冇好多甲亢都有嘅徵狀(手震、心跳快、眼凸)<br />\n我依家人係外國讀書，又就黎考試，唔知點算好，有啲擔心<br />\n想問下甲狀腺有問題係咪會甩頭髮，定係太大壓力<br />\n<br />\nPS 20歲女仔"},{"pid":"41cfe45a583373cc3240e504c4f41a36c2235073","tid":1183360,"uid":182314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T00:44:22.000Z","msg":"睇醫生咯，會開藥食住先，<br />\n問你做唔做手術，切唔切，<br />\n公立排隊做手術，起碼等1年，有期通知你"},{"pid":"be84d4ab01999b81b7bb84692a4caaa759004d07","tid":1183360,"uid":140234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T01:08:46.000Z","msg":"點解唔去睇門診<br />\n兩星期有結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31e920533c596b5792795456b05d8d63e3bc0dea","tid":1183360,"uid":256872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be84d4ab01999b81b7bb84692a4caaa759004d07","tid":1183360,"uid":140234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T01:08:46.000Z","msg":"點解唔去睇門診<br />\n兩星期有結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T01:20:47.000Z","msg":"因為我依家係外國讀緊書，又唔敢同屋企人講<br />\n驚佢地擔心"},{"pid":"c75a7dde398fec0830e88f16355c5dea24cd7071","tid":1183360,"uid":6845,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"31e920533c596b5792795456b05d8d63e3bc0dea","tid":1183360,"uid":256872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be84d4ab01999b81b7bb84692a4caaa759004d07","tid":1183360,"uid":140234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T01:08:46.000Z","msg":"點解唔去睇門診<br />\n兩星期有結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"re